<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>자기애 [자기애]</dt><br>
<dd>self-love; narcissism</dd><br>
<dd>자기 자신을 사랑하는 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>Excessive love toward oneself.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>자기도취 [자기도취]</dt><br>
<dd>narcissism; self-complacence</dd><br>
<dd>스스로에게 매우 만족하여 마치 홀린 듯이 깊이 빠지는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling very satisfied with oneself and falling into this feeling deeply, as if one was bewitched.</dd><br>
